front.title: Vine Snake
front.gametext: Habitat: planet sites (except Hoth). Attacks a character by attaching. X starts at 0. Every move phase, draw destiny; each time destiny > ability, add 1 to X. Character is power -X (eaten if power = 0).
front.lore: Found on various planets throughout the galaxy. Hides among hanging vines, dropping on unsuspecting travelers that pass beneath. Kills its victims through gradual constriction.
